		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-15e43d76 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4955ee76 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-tablet__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-jkit_accordion">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div  class="jeg-elementor-kit jkit-accordion style-default jeg_module_1074_10_69b7374b0c3fa"><div class="card-wrapper expand">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-aae80d4" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-aae80d4" aria-controls="expand-aae80d4">
                        <span class="title">1. What does ClimbHQ do?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-aae80d4" style="display:block"><div class="card-body"><p>Climbhq is a marketing agency that helps climbing centres grow through digital marketing, including social media management, paid advertising, SEO, content creation, and branding. We tailor our strategies to the climbing industry to attract more visitors and increase engagement.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-82fbab9" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-82fbab9" aria-controls="expand-82fbab9">
                        <span class="title">2. Do you only work with climbing centres?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-82fbab9" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>Yes! We specialise in the climbing industry, meaning we understand your audience, your challenges, and what works best to market your centre effectively.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-f4fc474" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-f4fc474" aria-controls="expand-f4fc474">
                        <span class="title">3. How can Climbhq help my climbing centre attract more customers?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-f4fc474" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>We use proven targeted digital marketing strategies like social media campaigns, search engine optimisation (SEO), and paid advertising to increase your visibility and drive more visitors to your centre. We also provide a specially designed marketing CRM to ensure all your customer data is stored and re-marketed to on a regular basis. </p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-c8a36ee" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-c8a36ee" aria-controls="expand-c8a36ee">
                        <span class="title">4. What makes Climbhq different from other marketing agencies?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-c8a36ee" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>Unlike general marketing agencies, we focus solely on the climbing industry. We know the market, the language, and the community, which allows us to create more authentic and effective marketing strategies.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-4256ca5" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-4256ca5" aria-controls="expand-4256ca5">
                        <span class="title">5. Do you offer one-time services or only ongoing packages?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-4256ca5" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>We offer a choice of packages that we have tested and know work for each centre's budget and goals. Whether you need a full-service ongoing marketing package or a one-time project like a website refresh or content creation, we can tailor our services to your needs.</p></div></div>
            </div></div>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-35ef4c53 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-tablet__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-jkit_accordion">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div  class="jeg-elementor-kit jkit-accordion style-default jeg_module_1074_11_69b7374b0cba9"><div class="card-wrapper expand">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-aae80d4" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-aae80d4" aria-controls="expand-aae80d4">
                        <span class="title">6. Can you help promote NICAS courses at my centre?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-aae80d4" style="display:block"><div class="card-body"><p>Absolutely! As NICAS partners, we can help you market your NICAS courses, making it easier to attract new climbers and grow your instructional programs.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-82fbab9" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-82fbab9" aria-controls="expand-82fbab9">
                        <span class="title">7. How do you measure success?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-82fbab9" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>Our most important metric is customers through the door. But we also provide in depth reports on key performance metrics such as website traffic, social media engagement, lead generation, and conversion rates.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-f4fc474" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-f4fc474" aria-controls="expand-f4fc474">
                        <span class="title">8. How much do your services cost?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-f4fc474" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>Our pricing varies depending on the package or service you choose. We offer flexible options to fit different budgets, from starter plans to full-scale marketing campaigns. Contact us for a quote tailored to your centre’s needs.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-c8a36ee" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-c8a36ee" aria-controls="expand-c8a36ee">
                        <span class="title">9. How long does it take to see results?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-c8a36ee" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>Some strategies, like paid ads, can drive immediate results, while others, like SEO and organic social media growth, take time to build momentum. We focus on sustainable, long-term success while also delivering quick wins.</p></div></div>
            </div><div class="card-wrapper ">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a href="#expand-1fc717a" class="card-header-button" aria-expanded="false" data-target="#expand-1fc717a" aria-controls="expand-1fc717a">
                        <span class="title">10. How do we get started?</span><div class="right-icon-group">
                <div class="normal-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-arrow-up-right-line"></i></div>
                <div class="active-icon"><i aria-hidden="true" class="jki jki-minus-solid"></i></div>
            </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-1fc717a" style="display:none"><div class="card-body"><p>Simple! Just reach out to us for a free consultation. We’ll discuss your goals, recommend the best approach, and create a strategy that fits your centre’s needs.</p></div></div>
            </div></div>				</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		
		
